pected random fraction, indicating that some pairs undergo correlated nuclear\nactivity. Taken together with complimentary studies, we favour an\ninterpretation where interactions trigger AGN, but are not the only cause of\nnuclear activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Aug 2011 20:08:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
